  m_text: "WASD - move                          Escape\nMouse - look                       
    to open/ close this \nT - activate transition\nLeft Mouse - shoot\nSpacebar -
    jump/ double jmp\nE - interact (open doors)\n\nEach Ammo Type deals different
    Damage and has different cooldown between shots;\nSmoke from back vent is cooldown
    indicator;\nCollect coloured spheres to unlock keys and the geometrical golden
    shapes to unlock ammo types;\n\n\n"
